"title": "6024: sin, effects of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6024: sin, effects of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sin affects every level of human existence, including the sinner's relationship with God, with other human beings and with the environment.</p>\n<h2>The effects of sin on individuals</h2>\n<h3>Lack of peace of mind</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:20-Isa57:21\">ISA 57:20–57:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:20-Job15:35\">JOB 15:20–15:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:5-Ps38:8\">PSA 38:5–38:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:15-Prov13:22\">PRO 13:15–13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:20-Lam1:21\">LAM 1:20–1:21</a></p>\n<h3>Bondage to a continuing habit of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:34\">JHN 8:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:22\">PRO 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:16\">ROM 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:16\">2TI 2:16</a></p>\n<h3>Physical death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:56\">1CO 15:56</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:17\">GEN 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:19\">GEN 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:16\">PRO 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:14\">ROM 5:12–5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:21-Rom6:23\">ROM 6:21–6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:15\">JAS 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>The sinful life is equivalent to death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1\">EPH 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:9\">ROM 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:13\">ROM 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:10\">ROM 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13\">COL 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>The effects of sin on the sinner before God</h2>\n<h3>Uncleanness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:6\">ISA 64:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:39\">PSA 106:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:22\">JER 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:8\">LAM 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:18-Matt15:20\">MAT 15:18–15:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:20-Mark7:23\">MRK 7:20–7:23</a></p>\n<h3>Guilt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:6\">EZR 9:6</a></strong> <em>The prayer of Ezra.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:10\">GEN 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:3-Ps38:4\">PSA 38:3–38:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:15\">PSA 44:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:12-Isa59:13\">ISA 59:12–59:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:25\">JER 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:20\">JER 14:20</a></p>\n<h3>Separation from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:2\">ISA 59:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:18\">DEU 31:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15\">ISA 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:7\">ISA 64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:6\">EZK 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:6\">HOS 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:4\">MIC 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:12\">EPH 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>The effects of sin on Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:34\">PRO 14:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:1-Josh7:16\">JOS 7:1–7:16</a> <em>Achan's sin</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:33-1Kgs8:40\">1KI 8:33–8:40</a> <em>the consequences of sin for Israel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:4-Isa1:9\">ISA 1:4–1:9</a> <em>the plight of Judah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21-Rom1:32\">ROM 1:21–1:32</a> <em>the condition of humanity</em></p>\n<h2>The effects of sin on the world</h2>\n<h3>The ground cursed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:18\">GEN 3:17–3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:13\">JER 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:20-Rom8:22\">ROM 8:20–8:22</a></p>\n<h3>The land polluted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:25\">LEV 18:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:10-Gen4:12\">GEN 4:10–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:33-Num35:34\">NUM 35:33–35:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:38\">PSA 106:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:4-Isa24:6\">ISA 24:4–24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:1\">JER 3:1</a></p>",
